Course Sailed

The tacks are supprisingly parallel. It seems the wind direction was relatively stable until later in the beat.

Apparent Wind Angle

For some reason, the appaprent wind angle [AWA] and apparent wind speed [AWS] stopped logging around 1:50PM. Unfortunately, this means many of the values calculated from AWA and AWS cant be used past this time. This includes the true wind and polar targets.

Apparent Wind Speed also stopped logging after some time.
